{"title":"七月抒怀（二首）","authors":["谢先云"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":7,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月抒怀（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢先云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望湘江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淳厚的两岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被你的心血渗透了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九曲回肠的步履"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日里夜里的呐喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在昨天的风暴里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见你水火相搏的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有荒草和路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时听不见你的笑声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我从老远赶来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不敢惊动你的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涛声已做了汽笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排浪已做了白帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在两岸的新话题里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又把梦幻的长臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥向丰实的秋天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窑洞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看青瘦和智慧的身影如何潇洒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映在窑洞的窗棂上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃一盏油灯就足够了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用一半亮在炕下思索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用一半亮在纸上描绘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后再留下一线灯光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听听明儿塬上飘来的信天游"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一屋轻烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一缸灰烬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明刚刚爬上窗棂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江山就从马背落在人心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窑洞在陕北"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陕北在中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油灯映着毛泽东的风采"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窑洞是中国的背景"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":10,"page_end":10}